    "abhinav": {
      "author": "Sri Abhinav Gupta",
      "et":
          "5.16 Jnanena etc.  When however the  Illusion is destroyed by  knowledge, then  the natural  capacity of  knowledge,  in illuminating  itself  and  other things starts to work automatically just as the sun does when the darkness is lost.  Indeed when the doubt  [of poison] is completely rooted out, the nectar does  the work of the nectar just automatically.\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n But  this is possible for  those who have their intellect and mind gone to This  [Self]  and have abandoned  [all]  other  activities.  To make this idea clear  [the Lord] says -",
      "sc":
          "।।5.16।।अत एव  ज्ञानेन त्विति।  ज्ञानेन तु अज्ञाने नाशिते ज्ञानस्य स्वपरप्रकाशकत्वं (K स्वप्रकाशकत्वं) स्वतःसिद्धम्  यथा आदित्यस्य तमसि नष्टे विनिवर्तितायां ( निवर्तितायां) हि शङ्कायाम् अमृतं अमृतकार्य स्वयमेव करोति।"
    },
